# --- Orphaned multi-agent swarm scaffolding ---
# The .agents/<phase> dirs (orchestrator/explorer/challenger/reviewer/auditor/
# implementer/sentinel + ORIGINAL_REQUEST.md) are a superseded Phase-1 swarm run;
# the real work lives on the committed Claude-plans/Codex-builds track. Keep the
# tracked project-installed design skills under .agents/skills/, ignore the rest.
/.agents/*
!/.agents/skills/
/agents/
.swarm/
ruvector.db
agentdb.rvf
agentdb.rvf.lock
