# --- Agent-runtime generated local state (2026-07-06 triage) ---
# Claude-flow/ruflo generated skill mirrors: ~60 dirs stamped by `ruflo init`.
# The four hand-authored skills committed before this rule stay tracked
# (gitignore never drops tracked files); `git add -f` any new deliberate skill.
.agents/skills/
# Codex co-agent scratch tree.
.codex/
# Session coverage/probe scratch logs at the .aios root.
.aios/cov_agent_*
.aios/fable_*
.aios/tmp_shots/
# Curriculum/mission runs generate arbitrary artifacts inside the sandbox
# work-tree (email_validator.py, test_string_reverser.py, ...). The curated
# sandbox files committed before this rule stay tracked (gitignore never
# affects tracked files); add a new deliberate sandbox file with `git add -f`.
training_ground/*
# lab/ is the short-name sandbox scope root (same posture as training_ground/,
# see aios/config.py SCOPE_ROOTS + aios/probe_common.py). Runtime seed
# fixtures from the learning-loop prover are ignored; lab/__init__.py and
# lab/conftest.py are force-added.
lab/*
